      <li><i class="fas fa-search"></i> <strong>Google Search</strong> ‚Äî How does it find results so quickly from billions of web pages?</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-video"></i> <strong>YouTube</strong> ‚Äî How does it store and stream millions of videos?</li>
      <li><i class="fas fa-shopping-cart"></i> <strong>Amazon</strong> ‚Äî How does it handle millions of products and orders?</li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <footer>
